>
  <article class="article">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">About</p>
      <h1>Longevity, decoded for life in Malaysia.</h1>
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>TheLongevityGPT answers one question well: <em>what actually adds healthy years?</em> Most longevity content online is hype, supplement ads, or biohacker folklore. We give clear, evidence-led answers, built for life in Malaysia and what you can actually buy here.</p>

        <h2>How we work</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Mechanism and evidence first.</strong> We explain <em>why</em> something might work, and how strong the human evidence actually is, before we get to any product or protocol.</li>
          <li><strong>Real comparisons.</strong> We weigh the actual options you can buy or do in Malaysia, side by side, on the same terms.</li>
          <li><strong>Local reality.</strong> Prices in ringgit, where to buy (Shopee, Watsons, Guardian, pharmacies), and what fits a hot, busy, urban life.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
        <p>Our content is educational. For persistent or worsening symptoms, or before starting a new supplement or protocol, see a doctor or pharmacist.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
